<li id="mwB6A"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt930" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book ","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Ricolfi"},"first":{"wt":"Luca"},"year":{"wt":"2005"},"contribution":{"wt":"Palestinians 1981–2003"},"editor-last":{"wt":"Gambetta"},"editor-first":{"wt":"Diego"},"title":{"wt":"Making Sense of Suicide Missions"},"edition":{"wt":"1st"},"location":{"wt":"Oxford"},"publisher":{"wt":"Oxford University Press"},"pages":{"wt":"76–130"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-19-927699-8"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwB6E">Ricolfi, Luca (2005). "Palestinians 1981–2003".  In Gambetta, Diego. <i id="mwB6I">Making Sense of Suicide Missions</i> (1st ed.). Oxford: Oxford University Press. pp.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwB6M"> </span>76–130. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwB6Q">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwB6U"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-19-927699-8" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-19-927699-8" id="mwB6Y">978-0-19-927699-8</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Palestinians+1981%E2%80%932003&amp;rft.btitle=Making+Sense+of+Suicide+Missions&amp;rft.place=Oxford&amp;rft.pages=76-130&amp;rft.edition=1st&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-19-927699-8&amp;rft.aulast=Ricolfi&amp;rft.aufirst=Luca&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATerrorism" class="Z3988" about="#mwt930" id="mwB6c"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt930" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwB6g"/></li></ul>
